<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-03-0521 </DOCNO><TEXT>Examination of the history of Government funding of nuclear and renewableenergy research in South Africa shows a bias towards nuclear energy.The areas of study in, and expenditure on, nuclear and renewable energyare outlined. The present and future role of these energy options isbriefly discussed. A comparison of funding of nuclear and renewable energyresearch in the United Kingdom is also given.</TEXT></DOC>